headline: Truckload earnings estimates cut heading into Q3 reports
summary: Susquehanna analyst Bascome Majors cut earnings forecasts on truckload carriers for the rest of the year as fundamentals remain soft and peak-season expectations are subdued. The post Truckload earnings estimates cut heading into Q3 reports appeared first on FreightWaves.

headline: Is C.H. Robinson Stock Outperforming the Nasdaq?
